No. 488,

Mise.

Irizarry y Puente v. President and Fellows of Harvard College et al. J. Irizarry y Puente, pro se. Charles B. Rugg, Oscar M. Shaw and James Vorenberg for respondents.

C. A. 1st Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Frankfurter took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
